body:
The `resource_handle.pb.h` is generated by the protobuf compiler, `protoc`.

It's either in
`$(MAKEFILE_DIR)/gen/protobuf-host/bin/protoc`
or somewhere on your path.

It should be generated [here](https://www.github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/Makefile#L544).

Please check if they're there, if not why aren't they generated, and if they are there, whether there is a problem in the include path.

/CC @satok16
